EDUCATIONAL USE DISCLAIMER:

This repository contains intentionally vulnerable code for educational purposes.
The vulnerable examples are designed to demonstrate security anti-patterns and
should NEVER be deployed to production environments or mainnet.

Always conduct thorough security audits before deploying smart contracts to
production. The authors and contributors are not liable for any losses incurred
from the use or misuse of this educational content.

For production deployments, only use the "secure" implementations and have them
audited by professional security firms.
